data.description: Nestled on a sprawling acre of land, this stunning home offers the perfect blend of country living and modern amenities. Boasting a spacious layout, this home features four bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. With 2,404 square feet of living space, this home offers plenty of room to spread out and relax. The swimming pool is the perfect addition for entertaining. One of the standout features of this property is the incredible mancave shop with electric 110 and 220 and AC This space offers ample storage and workspace, making it the ideal spot for all your projects and hobbies. In addition to the mancave shop, this property also includes a charming she shed with AC or can be used as an office separate from the home.. Located in an area with NO CITY TAXES, this property offers fiber optic internet service. Motivated sellers.
